data.description: *Price adjusted* This is perfect for who loves luxury, comfort and wants to live in a community that offers high-quality lifestyle. With over $62,000 in upgrades, this is a rare gem among the few 3 car garage homes available in the community. The gourmet kitchen package is the heart of the home with top-of-the-line appliances, stunning quartz countertops, and the under cabinet lights add a warm glow to the sleek cabinetry. The luxury bath package is equally impressive with double vanity, and elegant finishes. Throughout the house, you will find beautiful upgrades like 36'' laundry upper cabinets, LED lighting, and 5 1/4 crown molding. To top it off is the $30K premium lot with lake views. Imagine waking up each morning to the beauty of this view! Stop dreaming and come see this house.
